title: Evoland [v1.0.2278] (2013) PC ENG
description:
The game begins with no sound or music and only the Right Key available, but quickly takes the player through the earliest developments in video games: the Left Key, 2D Movement, Basic Scrolling and then Sounds FX! Soon, the player finds their first weapon, a sword and shortly thereafter, enters the world of 16 colors.
Discoveries such as monsters, combat and inventory all appear in due course as the player learns the evolution of video games.


Windows XP SP2 / 7 / 8
1.7 GHz
1 GB
Directx 9.0
